function Start(flMonstersKilledPct, idActorKiller, idActorKilled)

	-- announce the ambush, and make sure the target is valid	
	local idAmbushTarget = DF_KAM_AnnounceAmbush(idActorKiller)
	
	DF_Ambush("Ambush", "Skeleton", idActorKiller)
	DF_Ambush("Elite", "Skeleton", idActorKiller)
	
end

function Start(flMonstersKilledPct, idActorKiller, idActorKilled)

	-- announce the ambush, and make sure the target is valid	
	local idAmbushTarget = DF_KAM_AnnounceAmbush(idActorKiller)
	
	DF_Ambush("Ambush", "Demon", idActorKiller)
	DF_Ambush("Elite", "Demon", idActorKiller)
	
end

function Start(nMonstersRemaining, idActorKiller, idActorKilled)

	-- announce the ambush, and make sure the target is valid	
	local idAmbushTarget = DF_KAM_AnnounceAmbush(idActorKiller)
	
	DF_Ambush("Elite", "Demon", idActorKiller)
	DF_Ambush("Ambush", "Demon", idActorKiller)
	
	-- waiting after this one, we're vacuuming the last 10 mobs 
	-- the ambush needs a beat to spawn and get added to the KAM actor group
	Hydra.Wait(0.01)
	
	DF_KAM_CullFarthestMonsters(10, S_KAM_VACUUMED)

end

function Start(flGameTime)

	-- if this is the very first phase, the phase starts before everything is ready, wait a beat 
	-- before spawning markers and checking distances, etc.
	if bInitialized == nil then
		Hydra.Wait(1)
		DF_KAM_Initialize(S_KAM_MARKER)
	end

	-- pull abandoned monsters to a player
	DF_KAM_HeartBeat_Cull(S_KAM_MARKER, S_KAM_VACUUMED)
	
end

function Start(idActorKiller, idActorKilled)
	Hydra.BossEncounterManuallyComplete(Hydra.ReferenceLevelArea(idBossLevelArea))
	
	--Play Boss Victory Stinger
	Hydra.MusicOverride("DGN_Hawe_AncientReservoir", "Music_Boss_Skeleton_Victory")

	--Wait for Stinger to resolve and Reset Dungeon Music
	Hydra.Wait(10)
	Hydra.ClearMusicOverride("DGN_Hawe_AncientReservoir")	
end

function Start(idActorPlayer, idActorGizmo)

	-- Get the Level Area.
	idBossLevelArea = Hydra.ActorGetLevelArea(idActorGizmo)
	
	-- Once the Monolith is done start the fight.
	Hydra.Wait(3)
	Hydra.BossEncounterManuallyQueueStart(Hydra.ReferenceLevelArea(idBossLevelArea))		
	
end

function AmbushTarget()

	local tPlayers = Hydra.PlayerActors()
	
	local tValidTargets = {}
	for iter, idPlayer in pairs(tPlayers) do
		if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idPlayer) --[[and Hydra.ActorIsAlive(idPlayer)]] then
			table.insert(tValidTargets, idPlayer)
		end
	end
	
	ShuffleTable(tValidTargets)
	
	return tValidTargets[1]
end

function HordeTrigger()

	local idAmbushLocation = AmbushTarget()
	Hydra.ActorSpawnActor(S_SPAWNER_AMBUSH, idAmbushLocation, true, 2, 4, Hydra.MR_NORMAL, Hydra.PowerSNOFromName(Hydra.ReferencePower("Summoned_Animating_FromGroundPortal_NoFadeIn")))
	
end
